      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 standard test condition (quasi-static, room temperature, ambient environment). Only one test condition was evaluated, yielding an achieved level of 2 against the required level of 3 for Medium model risk. This factor is below the required level and is noted as a credibility gap; it is accepted based on the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the availability of clinical performance data supporting the design."
