      "rationale": "Acceptance bounds (<10% QoI difference, E/uval < 1.96) were pre-specified in the validation plan prior to unblinding of experimental results. All three QoIs (stiffness: 4.2%, yield force: 6.8%, force at 40 mm: 7.5%) fall within the percent difference bound. All E/uval values (0.87, 1.21, 1.44) fall below 1.96. The comparison methodology is fully quantitative and pre-registered."
